namespace pdg { /**

\fn pdg::Sprite::onMouseDown

\brief set event handler for finger down or mouse down in this sprite

Only works if you first call setWantsClickEvents(true).

\note if you are just looking for a click on a sprite-base button, see onMouseClick(), which handles the mouse down and mouse up events for you.

\sa setWantsClickEvents()
\sa onMouseUp()
\sa onMouseClick()
\sa SpriteTouchEvent
\sa IEventHandler

**/ }